---
title: Find the Best Home-Service Companies in North Texas (2026)
description: Independent rankings of the best HVAC, plumbing, roofing and electrical companies in Dallas–Fort Worth — scored on a published methodology with sourced figures. No paid placement.
layout: base.njk
permalink: /best/
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1>Find the best pros in North Texas</h1>
  <p class="lede">Every ranking scores real local companies on verified ratings, experience, pricing transparency, warranty and licensing — figures sourced from public profiles, updated monthly, and <strong>no company pays for placement</strong>. Read the full <a href="/methodology/">methodology</a>.</p>
</section>

{% if collections.rankings.length %}
<section>
  <h2 class="sec-title">By trade</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    {% for r in collections.rankings %}
    <a class="card" href="{{ r.url }}">
      <h3>{{ r.data.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ r.data.cardBlurb }}</p>
      <span class="meta-row"><span class="tag">{{ r.data.placement }}</span><span class="updated">Updated {{ r.data.updated | readableDate }}</span></span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if collections.reviews.length %}
<section>
  <h2 class="sec-title">HVAC, city by city</h2>
  <p class="sec-sub">Cooling is DFW's biggest home-system expense, so HVAC gets the deepest coverage — one ranking per city.</p>
  <div class="cards">
    {% for r in collections.reviews %}
    <a class="card" href="{{ r.url }}">
      <h3>Best HVAC in {{ r.data.cityName }}</h3>
      <p>{{ r.data.cardBlurb }}</p>
      <span class="meta-row"><span class="tag">{{ r.data.placement }}</span><span class="updated">Updated {{ r.data.updated | readableDate }}</span></span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}
